    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023540/extras/514c5ad796f6ac69dc1af41aeea0a5a2.avif?t=1771976943\" width=600 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Tapes of Fear: Smile（恐惧录音带：微笑）</strong></i> 的唯一目标就是让你感受到最大的恐惧。这款第一人称心理恐怖游戏确保每次游玩都能带来独特而可怕的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023540/extras/cee6dea4614e438cd74ee1acb6f1dcdd.avif?t=1771976943\" width=600 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <i>Tapes of Fear</i> 的核心是创新的 <strong>Infinity Fear System™（无限恐惧系统）</strong>，由 Infinity Green Game Studio 打造的技术。基于关于如何引发恐惧的学术研究开发，这一先进系统会实时监控你的决策和反应，动态调整游戏事件以最大化恐怖效果。该系统确保你不会遭遇过多或过少的惊吓，从而保持完美的恐怖节奏。每个决策和反应都会改变事件进程，每次游玩都带来全新的恐怖体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023540/extras/5a055602ff5b53290257d6c03be3ef92.poster.avif?t=1771976943\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023540/extras/5a055602ff5b53290257d6c03be3ef92.webm?t=1771976943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023540/extras/5a055602ff5b53290257d6c03be3ef92.mp4?t=1771976943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SMILE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 你并非孤身一人——你在一座陌生的房子中醒来，发现自己被困其中。一位始终挂着诡异笑容的黑暗实体利用墙壁间的管道不停地追捕你。这个敌人无情且适应性强，每次遭遇都演变成一场生存之战。它的持续存在让你时刻保持高度警惕；你的角色完全无力反抗，只能运用智慧和敏捷来避免被发现。 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023540/extras/0a1adc965439f62a646745fefd6802c3.poster.avif?t=1771976943\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023540/extras/0a1adc965439f62a646745fefd6802c3.webm?t=1771976943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023540/extras/0a1adc965439f62a646745fefd6802c3.mp4?t=1771976943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >理智</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在 <i>Tapes of Fear</i> 中保持理智对生存至关重要。房子里充满了扰乱身心的事件，会对你的角色造成心理和生理双重影响。寻找、使用并管理各种有助于你稳定理智的道具。 <strong>准备好踏上一段在 <i>Tapes of Fear</i> 中考验你的心智和勇气的旅程吧。每次游玩都是全新的恐怖体验，保证让你永远无法完全预知接下来会发生什么。</strong></p>",
